data.title: Kofi Annan during his Younger Years as a Student
data.meta_description:
Kofi Annan, Secretary-General of the United Nations (right) breaking 12 year record for the 60 yards sprint at Carleton Stadium at Macalester College, during his younger years as student.
	
	[1960 or 1961]
	01 January 1960
	St. Paul, United States
	Photo # 1091
